nodes.bodyText: I am not sure this should be converted - a) it is not enabled by default right now and seems a bit spurious and b) it isn't really unimplemented - it just doesn't do anything. @mpirvu do you know what the fate of this assert should be?

This is more of a "we should never get here for JITServer". So the correct implementation is:
TR_ASSERT_FATAL(false, "profilingSample(pc...) should not be called on JITServer");
